# Locked: ERP display (photos + stock)

- **Canonical doc:** [`docs/infra/ERP_DISPLAY_LOCKED.md`](docs/infra/ERP_DISPLAY_LOCKED.md)

- **Product photos:** Do not remove `product-images/` prefix stripping in [`productImageUpload.ts`](src/app/utils/productImageUpload.ts). Do not change [`deploy/nginx.conf`](deploy/nginx.conf) static file regex without `(?!storage/)` exclusion. Keep PWA `skipWaiting` / `clientsClaim` unless user approves cache regressions.

- **Stock qty on UI:** Overview grids/reports must use [`inventoryService.getInventoryOverview`](src/app/services/inventoryService.ts). When `stock_movements` exist for the company, do **not** read `inventory_balance` for displayed qty on simple products. Ledger lines use `getStockMovements`; header qty must match overview.

- **Mobile:** Native image URLs follow [`docs/infra/MOBILE_APK_LOCKED_PATTERN.md`](docs/infra/MOBILE_APK_LOCKED_PATTERN.md).

If the user reports wrong thumbs, HTML 404 on storage upload, or stock 0 on grid vs 1 in ledger, read `ERP_DISPLAY_LOCKED.md` verification checklists first, then propose a **minimal** fix with explicit approval.
